Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大清早的就练拳么  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fsp163}　{\fsp0}Magia Erebea{\r}\N据说是依文洁琳从前写下的黑暗魔法的卷轴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.10,0:00:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…并不是普通的咒文卷轴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「如果你要走光明大道就不要打开」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「如果选择黑暗的话就打开看看」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你早就已经决定好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样  我也在好好看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这点事我看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「父亲的道路  还是师父的道路！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何  决定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  光明和黑暗  你选哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:02:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  你果然还是想走你父亲的路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这也不无道理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千雨同学  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个选择或许真的很乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会还在犹豫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是对是错  不做做看怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这是个重大决定  我能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那是你自己选择的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己走出的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管它乱来不乱来的  拿出自信来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好见证的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我的心意已决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深思熟虑后的结论  或许是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会被黑暗吞没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了今后也能和大家一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了追上父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿放手一搏…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉坎先生  我选择黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真出人意料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过小子  你不用追你父亲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是父亲  怎么模仿也不能成为他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我有黑暗的潜力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只有穷究这一潜力  才能追上父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也…很喜欢师父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱的告白啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可你太小看黑暗了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那卷轴  一旦打开了它  可是会很艰苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这卷轴非同寻常这点我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经做好觉悟了  一定会突破难关的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你说的哦  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就让你好好体会到黑暗可不容你小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克服这一难关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果挺不过去你就只有一死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么回事  为什么她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了  会很艰苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  要塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑快跑  不然要被活埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到最后会碰到这么老套的陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  你还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快看  是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好险呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到遗迹会整个崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为会死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说来  你真的变坚强了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在遗迹里发现的你说要加入我们的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真不知道该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯  和香发现陷阱的能力一级棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能派用场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个年纪就有这等能力  你究竟是在哪学到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  是在课外活动上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  期待已久的分赃时间到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不枉我们辛苦  收获颇丰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  你真的不要财宝？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不用了  我要这个就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要卖的话  应该也很值钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是和香在找的魔法道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  多亏了各位  终于得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fsp220}　{\fsp0}Comptina  Daemonia{\r}\N能看穿对方名字的魔法道具「鬼神童谣」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍有点坏坏的感觉～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有二十米长的大块头却有如此高的机动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外加充沛的体力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  龙真是个强大的种族  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫忍法  缚锁爆炎阵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不动明王真言  不动一字咒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（梵文）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫不会被黑龙打败了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,击退黑龙的任务完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下手有些太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮它治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不胜感激
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  注意不要把一边的角也治好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,东风桧扇  南风末广
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  能治愈那么大的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙  伤治好了还要再干一场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香  快退下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能再做坏事啦  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别再回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  按照委托  把它的一支角折断了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在明年重新长出角来之前  它应该不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来  木乃香你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢  你称赞我也没好处的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要这么说的话  枫才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戴着眼罩能赢过龙  这是有多强？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  这是修行的一环…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这点本事还完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  枫你不也受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你治好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来木乃香的治愈术越来越娴熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开门  开门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那不是黑龙的角吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两位干得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眯眯眼的大姐  传言你就是真正的忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相比之下  住在我们店里的这两个窝囊废…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我们吧  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是黑龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  袭击村子的两条龙中  只击退了其中一条
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  听说有其他旅行中的赏金猎人击退了另外一条
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:12:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚些要来我们店里啊  请你们吃一顿边境最好吃的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在原本的世界中我的能力毫无用场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到在这里竟然能让人们这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很少见到木乃香那么沮丧的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我并没有…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  涅吉小弟也会平安无事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那和明日菜一定也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神来啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  大小姐确实在这一带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们却为了打败龙而浪费了时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说这支角能卖大价钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小木…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜别来无恙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹  小刹  我好想你啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大  大大大  大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜你也没事真太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦  木乃香你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  这下涅吉魔社四人汇合了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不明白怎么回事  总之祝贺你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜又变强了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得出吗  枫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在做赏金猎人时不仅打倒魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还反击了袭击我们的赏金猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  接下来就差和涅吉还有大家汇合了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  烧退不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这和之前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那女人到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有她去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人？  是说长得像依文一样的家伙么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是依文的劣化复制品  人造灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在估计在小子体内呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让他能运用黑暗力量而给他试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小子如果不能经受住这场试炼  就再也不会醒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少他的身体将不能再使用魔法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没听说这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你既然知道  就应该阻止…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不正常的方法  这点风险应该早就做好觉悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做好准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准备的话可是会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是精神上的死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}　Ensis Exsequens{\r}\N哦  断罪之剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是在模仿我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  你不也从一开始就有战斗的打算么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到竟然有愚蠢到自己选择黑暗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地点变了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我要冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里大概是我的脑内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个师父应该也不是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗是什么  小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与光相反的影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与白昼相反的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生与死  善与恶  秩序与混沌  合理与不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  在这里你所需要的是更单纯的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,lic lac la lac lilac
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}veniant spiritus glaciales{\r}\N来吧  冰之精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}extendantur aeri{\r}\N充满于大气之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}tundram et glaciem loci noctis albae{\r}\N带来白夜之国的冻土与冰河吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Crystallizatio Tellustris　{\r}\N冻结的大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那既是吞噬一切的黑洞  也是原初的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是次元的混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,lic lac la lac lilac
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  冰精！来吧  风精！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Nivis Casus　{\r}\N冰爆！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能理解其中道理  你就会在这里被我杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬一切的原初的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要冷静  这个师父不过是由我的记忆和想象造出的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是我的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依我的印象  我对师父的印象…对师父的印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,印…象…完全赢不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  你其实早已理解其中意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂寸劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了  我忘了要留地方立足了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬动！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千钧一发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  是不是做得过火了点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  今天也向前迈进了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不能停止修行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是啥东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古菲同学  我找你找得可辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是不显眼的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好过分  古菲同学你好坏好坏好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家那么努力找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗  小夜崽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…啊  早已死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你能在那么大的世界里找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是自己一个人  是怎么做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  小弟  已经不行了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是几百个小时罢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个师父是我的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战胜她也就意味着战胜我自己的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  要怎么打败她！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Sagitta Magica Series Fulguralis{\r}\N魔法之射手  雷之九矢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雷华崩拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真让我惊讶  你竟然还能有如此的行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fsp340}　{\fsp0}Phantasmagoria{\r}\N在这无法入眠  无法逃避  甚至不允许死亡的幻想空间里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能坚持这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意志力堪称奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的精神力也会迎来极限的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第几次了  七十次左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回你还能站得起来吗  小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  大叔  药草不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再给我点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  小姐  你也够厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然两天两夜不睡  照顾着小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙要是出了什么事  有一半是我的责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这到底要持续多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么久了  很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  不说肉体上的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,精神上说不定真的已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Phantasmagoria{\fsp65}　{\r}\N现在小子所在的幻想空间的感觉时间是现实的几倍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算下来他至少持续战斗了十天以上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,常人已经无法保持自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小子已经很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十天？那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fsp135}　{\fsp0}Phantasmagoria{\r}\N没错  如果小子再找不出突破幻想空间的方法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他就出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我之前所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要么再也醒不过来  要么再也不能用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天破晓时大概就是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐你也做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来  通向光明和黑暗的两条路都断了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你的同伴救活你  回到家里  忘了你父亲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个学园里和大家一起快乐地活下去也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:22:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得很好了  小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Nivis Casus　{\r}\N冰爆！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  终于势均力敌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看着  好好品尝  好好记住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的力量源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你本能的冲动  你最大的动力  你的心象风景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你还赢不了  真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.03,0:22:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被打败了  这样还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也理所当然  我怎么可能打败师父…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这笨蛋涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  夸下那么大的海口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:22:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,lic lac la lac lilac
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}veniant spiritus glaciales obscurantes　{\r}\N来吧  冰精！暗之精灵！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}cum obscurationi flet tempestas nivalis　{\r}\N听令于黑暗吹起永夜的冰雪吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  明日菜同学  我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  你其实早已理解其中意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  对啊  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了  小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Nivis Tempestas Obscurans　{\r}\N暗夜吹雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就在大家对我说的话语之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有再大的烦恼也别去在意  把它藏在心底前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是怨恨别人  逃避事实而得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是你足以引以为傲的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使摔得一身是泥  仍然要向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.01,0:23:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Magia Erebea{\fsp77}　{\r}\N黑暗魔法  那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.26,0:24:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论善还是恶  坚强还是弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都原封不动地接受并吞噬掉的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.89,0:24:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Complexio　{\r}\N掌握！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不错啊  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.37,0:24:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fsp23}　{\fsp0}Magia Erebea{\r}\N终于学会黑暗魔法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是由我的记忆构成的我的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.53,0:24:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即是我的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.45,0:24:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒你并不代表就通过这个试炼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.71,0:24:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你花太多时间了  不过我也不追究了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.87,0:24:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的成果吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.21,0:25:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.35,0:25:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.10,0:25:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经等不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.19,0:25:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天开始亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.44,0:25:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要用那把匕首取消试炼的话  必须在日出之前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.21,0:25:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.82,0:25:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…果然还是不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.97,0:25:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了  老师  我没能相信你到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.11,0:25:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要你没事的话  还有很多方法可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.60,0:25:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  千雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.95,0:25:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.89,0:26:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.31,0:26:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千雨同学  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.87,0:26:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要醒就给我早点醒啊  你这臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.50,0:26:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然像故事里一样  在最后的最后才醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.44,0:26:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.40,0:26:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  很危险的…千雨同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.38,0:26:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知不知道浪费了我多少感情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.41,0:26:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  等等…我不知道为什么浑身都痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.97,0:26:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.08,0:26:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.51,0:26:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  你醒啦  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.04,0:26:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉坎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.87,0:26:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔  你这什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.78,0:26:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是不得已陪了他整整两天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.94,0:26:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等  很危险的啊  千雨小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.64,0:26:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是谁  看到他平安都该掉两滴眼泪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.40,0:26:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.81,0:26:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  小子  要好好感谢她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.38,0:27:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她照顾了濒死的你整整两天两夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.76,0:27:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  千雨同学她…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.15,0:27:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千雨同学  谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.34,0:27:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  别以为一句道谢就能还清这笔债！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.24,0:27:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我跪下  成为我的奴隶！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.57,0:27:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样  你做得很好  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.69,0:27:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样总算站上起跑线了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.01,0:27:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你把魔力集中到双臂上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.56,0:27:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,双臂…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.65,0:27:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是习得依文的黑暗魔法的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.82,0:27:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己习得的  只属于你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.69,0:27:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为此骄傲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.39,0:27:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,习得师父的技能的证明…！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.74,0:27:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但不要懈怠了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.81,0:27:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不过是刚刚得到了自己的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.12,0:27:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是今后
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.39,0:28:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.52,0:28:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那就马上走吧  让我看看你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.64,0:28:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.50,0:28:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…喂  说什么马上  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.46,0:28:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  千雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.66,0:28:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.41,0:28:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…十分感谢你
